programme.title: Godsend
programme.desc: Efter deras unga sons dod kommer Paul och Jessie Duncan overens om att få honom klonad av en mystisk lakare. Saker och ting tar en olycksbådande vandning nar deras nya son vaxer upp och de lar sig en chockerande hemlighet om lakaren.

programme.title: Jungle
programme.desc: Den unge, israeliske Yossi Ghinsberg lamnar en trygg framtid bakom sig for folja en osannolik drom som for honom in i Amazonas regnskogs mystiska djup.. Under ett års tid gor han en resa som många innan honom har gjort men nar han blir bekant med två andra aventyrare, Kevin Gale och Marcus Stamm och de tre moter den morka och karismatiske Karl Ruchprecter foljer de med honom in i djungeln. Vad som borjar som forverkligandet av en drom forvandlas snart till ett hemskt och psykologiskt test av fortroende och mod. Den sanna historien om att overleva mot alla odds, baserad på Yossi Ghinsbergs memoarer.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Transference
programme.desc: Josh ar alltid på sin vakt, konstant paranoid och lever ett valdigt anstrangt liv. Allt pga att han håller sin valdigt storda syster gomd i en hemlig bunker, for att hemlighålla hennes overnaturliga krafter ifrån omvarlden. Nar hon en dag blir sjuk tvingas Josh anlita en vetenskapsman for att sakerstalla hennes halsa. Det blir ett odesdigert beslut som leder till att hennes superkrafter nu avslojas.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: 12 Rounds 3: Lockdown
programme.desc: WWE-superstjarnan Dean Ambrose spelar Shaw, en polis som återvander till aktiv tjanst efter partnerns dod. Nar han upptacker bevis som kopplar hans kolleger till mord, satter de dit honom for ett mord han inte har begått.

programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Saknad i strid (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikanska soldater hålls fångna i Vietnam — och det ar upp till en man att fora hem dem i denna fartfyllda action/aventyrsfilm med kampsportslegenden Chuck Norris. Efter en djarv flykt från ett krigsfånglager ar overste James Braddock (Norris) på ett uppdrag att lokalisera och radda saknade soldater med hjalp av en tjansteman från utrikesdepartementet (Lenore Kasdorf) och en tidigare armekompis (M. Emmet Walsh). Denna enmansarme ar redo att ta sig in i Vietnam… men kan han ta sig ut igen?

programme.title: Saints and Soldiers: Airborne Creed
programme.desc: Den 15 augusti 1944 hoppar en pluton från 517:e amerikanska fallskarmsregementet ner over sodra Frankrike. Deras uppdrag ar att bistå och skydda de allierade styrkorna i deras marsch mot Berlin, men nar de landar mitt i ett fientligt territorium blir de genast attackerade. Tre av fallskarmsjagarna isoleras från gruppen och i ett forsok att slutfora uppdraget och mote upp sin enhet stoter de på en desperat grupp ur den franska motståndsrorelsen. De bestammer sig for att hjalpa till att befria några av de tillfångatagna rebellerna – ett forsok dar de satter sina egna liv på spel. Genom att gora så handlar de i linje med regementets hederskodex – Airborne Creed.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Trinity klipper till igen
programme.desc: Men hor och hapna: Nu har de slagit sig på en karriar som hemliga poliser, med uppdrag att satta fast ett storsmugglande banditgang. For bra for att vara sant? Ja faktiskt, for de ar sjalva ute efter att håva in formogenheten. Och for att vinna guld kommer de offra mycket bly.Men till skillnad från andra vilda fighter och skottdueller finns har många vinnare. Vapentillverkare, bandageforsaljare och dodgravare till exempel. Och framforallt lakarna som måste ta hand om alla som skrattat kakarna ur led! Terence Hill and Bud Spencer ar ett av filmhistoriens popularaste hjaltepar, som dunkat skurkar ihop I nitton filmer!

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. Tillsammans bildar de tre en trio tillfalliga banditer nar de reser genom hela Nya Zeeland i en "lånad" gul Mini Cooper och ifrågasatter samhallets likriktning och jagar forlorad karlek med ett massivt polisuppbåd och varsta mediacirkusen hack i hal.

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Lonnmordaren Frank har lagt sitt tidigare arbete på hyllan och forsoker leva ett till synes vanligt liv tillsammans med flickvannen och hans dotter. En dag kommer en okand maffia boss forbi for att få Franks hjalp att ha ihjal den som tagit livet av hans unga dotter. For att inte dra in sin egen familj i eventuella komplikationer måste Frank fatta ett beslut om att gora stoten åt bossen eller få ro med sin egen sjal?

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: En astronomiprofessor som jobbat for NASA inser att en destruktiv asteroid ar på kollisionskurs med jorden och måste få sin familj i sakerhet samtidigt som han varnar varlden for denna hotande forodelse.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Hardcore
programme.desc: Du minns ingenting av ditt tidigare liv. Allt du vet ar att du heter Henry, något din fru berattade nar hon nyss återupplivade dig från de doda. Bara några minuter senare blir du beskjuten och din fru kidnappas. Den skyldige till dådet ar Akan, en maktig krigsherre omgiven av en arme av legosoldater, som planerar att ta over varlden. Plotsligt befinner du dig i Moskva dar alla vill se dig dod. Alla utom en mystisk engelsman, Jimmy. Men kan du verkligen lita på honom? Om du bara overlever vansinnet kommer du forstå meningen med allt och sanningen bakom din identitet. Lycka till Henry – du kommer sannolikt behova det…

programme.title: Skumma polare
programme.desc: Trinityseriens stjarna Bud Spencer återvander till vilda vastern i regissoren Michele Lupo’s komedi om bedragaren Buddy, som misstas for en lakare efter att hans van Cocoa oavsiktligt stjal en resvaska med kirurgiska instrument. Buddy bosatter sig i den lilla staden som en experimentell lakare. Nar ett gang våldsamma brottslingar forsoker ta over staden, visar det sig att hans sanna talang ar att slå ner skurkar synkad till musik som humoristiskt komponerats av spaghettivastmastaren Ennio Morricone.

programme.title: Saknad i strid 2 (Missing in Action 2: The Beginning)
programme.desc: Actionstjarnan Chuck Norris återvander som overste James Braddock i denna intensiva, actionfyllda prequel till den ursprungliga succefilmen. Nar kriget rasar i Vietnam blir Braddock och hans man tillfångatagna under en raddningsoperation i luften och fangslade av den hansynslose overste Yin (Soon-Tek Oh), som inte kommer att stoppa for något for att bryta deras anda! For Braddock ar valet klart: han måste befria sina medfångar och forstora lagret! Med navar, kraftiga sprangamnen och ren mod blir han en arme for sig sjalv!

programme.title: USS Indianapolis: Men of Courage
programme.desc: I slutet av andra varldskriget fraktade den amerikanska tunga kryssaren USS Indianapolis i hemlighet en av de två atombomber som skulle komma att avsluta kriget. En japansk ubåt anfoll och sankte fartyget. USS Indianapolis uppdrag var så hemligt att fartyget inte anmaldes saknat och ingen visste att fartyget hade sankts forran forst fyra dagar senare. Av de 1197 ombord foljde nastan 300 med sitt fartyg i djupet. De overlevande blev liggande i de hajrika vattnen i Filippinska sjon och tvingades att utstå hunger, torst, hetta, hallucinationer, ideliga hajangrepp och många av sina skeppskamraters dod. Fem dagar senare levde bara 317 man och dessa kunde till slut raddas.

programme.title: Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Europe`s Forgotten Pilgrim Routes: Switzerland, Italy: The VIA FRANCIGENA to Rome
programme.desc: For centuries, pilgrims have set off on the Via Francigena in the hopes of reaching the tombs of the apostles Peter and Paul in Rome. The ancient pilgrimage route leads through the imposing Alps to the Great St Bernard Pass and from there cross-country through Italy.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Over the Islands of Africa, Zanzibar
programme.desc: Photographer Matthias Ziegler is an Africa specialist. He has visited nearly every country on the continent on assignments for international agencies. Zanzibar, however, is new territory for him. Hes come to the former slave island for a photo book – and this time hes not alone. To see the Tanzanian archipelago from the air, he has enlisted the services of ultralight pilot Richard Meredith-Hardy of England to fly him around in his FIB, or flying inflatable boat. Perfect conditions for an adventurous journey: as a world champion ultralight pilot, Richard and his FIB can take off and land practically anywhere – in theory.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Over the Islands of Africa, Mauritius
programme.desc: Renaud Van Der Meeren is a photographer and paramotor pilot. With his motorised parachute he goes on expeditions to the remotest corners on earth to photograph people and landscapes from the air. Renaud wanted to be a jet pilot, studied music at the Sorbonne, became a ski instructor, model and photographers assistant before he found happiness in his current vocation. He especially likes to do his job in Mauritius – nowhere else does he find so many motifs as on the "sweetest pearl in the Indian Ocean". This time hes working on a photo book about Mauritius – by land, by water and in the air.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Over the Islands of Africa, Madagascar
programme.desc: Spirits, Kings, Lemurs – Madagascar treats Ami to a multitude of new impressions and spectacular pictures. Director Christian Schidlowski and his team accompanied her on her trip.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Over the Islands of Africa, Sao Tome and Principe
programme.desc: Along with photographer Rui Camilo, we travel to the West African island nation of Sao Tome and Príncipe - in search of images that will capture the soul of this small and beautiful country.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Over the Islands of Africa, Cape Verde
programme.desc: Cape Verde – the islands of Saudade, of longing. For Stephane and Richard it was a journey full of adventure, unforgettable encounters and magnificent photographs. Director Christian Schidlowski and his team accompanied them on their trip.

programme.title: Myths of the Congo - Apes and Aliens
programme.desc: The Congo, mighty and deep like no other river - yet still a retreat and a habitat for several of our worlds strangest animals. Our closest relatives live deep inside the dense jungles: three of the four giant ape species have made the Congo basin their home. Rich in extraordinary footage, the second episode of "Myths of the Congo" also presents exciting insights into one of the most mysterious and dangerous regions on earth.

programme.title: Myths of the Congo - Deep and Dangerous
programme.desc: The river that swallows all rivers - this is what the natives call it. In reality, the Congo, when considering its water masses, is the second largest and the deepest river in the world. At its source in the north of Zambia, it starts out as a mere trickle, but on its journey westwards it grows and grows, becoming ever mightier and with it, the animals, too: the shoebill stork hides in the dense papyrus. Metre-long pythons hunt for their prey in trees and huge hippos fight for power and respect in the water. To survive in the Congo, animals have to adapt to extreme conditions. Here, evolution has spawned unique creatures: fish with lungs, wings and those that go hunting on land. The Congo...

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The Parque Nacional Peneda-Geres is the only national park in Portugal. An area of almost 700 square kilometers, located in the extreme north of Portugal. Barren and rocky ridges in the plateaus, contrast with large forests and lush ground vegetation in deep valleys, crossed by lakes and rivers. The park is known for its oak forests, which are predominantly pedunculate and Pyrenean oaks. Among the typical animals of the park are the small Garrano ponies, a very old breed of horse and the only one in Europe that still lives in the wild.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The highest mountain range in Portugal is the Serra da Estrela. The episode embarks on a voyage of discovery to adventurous rock formations and villages steeped in tradition. The nature park is the largest protected area on the Iberian peninsula. In the mountain range we accompany the young scientist Ana Matos, who wants to breathe new life into old traditions, and cheese maker Maria Natália Lopes. She watches over more than 350 sheeps.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 South West Portugal: Alentejano and Costa Vicentina
programme.desc: In the southwest of Portugal lies the little known Parque Natural do Sudoeste Alentejano e Costa Vicentina. It encompasses a narrow coastal strip that runs along the coast to the south of Portugal. Sparsely populated, this coastal region, which was placed under protection in 1988, is considered one of the last intact ecosystems in Europe. The steep cliffs, the almost constant wind and high waves have ensured that mass tourism has not gained a foothold here. There are still near-natural forests and a diverse bird life.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: Madeira - Portugals autonomous island in the Atlantic Ocean, is closer to the African coast than to the mother country Portugal, from which it is separated by about 900 kilometers. The islands name comes from Portuguese sailors who claimed the uninhabited isle for themselves in 1419. Madeira means wood and that was available in abundance. Almost the entire surface was covered by dense forest. Since 1982, two-thirds of the landscape has been protected.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The "Parque Natural da Ria Formosa" is one of the largest lagoon conservation areas in Europe. Bordered by five natural islands. A mosaic of sandbanks, brackish and freshwater lagoons and salt marshes. In 2010, the "Ria Formosa" was chosen as one of the seven natural wonders of Portugal. It is a unique ecosystem: in the winter months, more than 20,000 birds gather here. In addition, the nature park has one of the largest seahorse populations internationally. More than half of all fish species in the Atlantic are said to spawn in the lagoon.

programme.title: Stories of the Mediterranean Forest: Sierra Morena
programme.desc: The Mediterranean Basin is one of the planet’s most biologically rich and complex regions. The crossroads of Europe, Asia and Africa is considered to be one of Earth’s biodiversity hotspots. A vast number of both animal and plant species unique to the region live in its various habitats. The Mediterranean Basin is located in one of the planet’s temperate zones. The subtropical climate makes it colder and wet here in winter, hot and dry in summer and mild and rainy in autumn and spring.

programme.title: The Canary Islands - In the Shadows of the Volcanoes
programme.desc: The Canary Islands were born in the depths of the ocean. Forged by fire and sculpted by winds and waves, this volcanic land offers landscapes of colossal force and almost unreal beauty.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Over the Islands of Africa, Zanzibar
programme.desc: Photographer Matthias Ziegler is an Africa specialist. He has visited nearly every country on the continent on assignments for international agencies. Zanzibar, however, is new territory for him. Hes come to the former slave island for a photo book – and this time hes not alone. To see the Tanzanian archipelago from the air, he has enlisted the services of ultralight pilot Richard Meredith-Hardy of England to fly him around in his FIB, or flying inflatable boat. Perfect conditions for an adventurous journey: as a world champion ultralight pilot, Richard and his FIB can take off and land practically anywhere – in theory.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Over the Islands of Africa, Mauritius
programme.desc: Renaud Van Der Meeren is a photographer and paramotor pilot. With his motorised parachute he goes on expeditions to the remotest corners on earth to photograph people and landscapes from the air. Renaud wanted to be a jet pilot, studied music at the Sorbonne, became a ski instructor, model and photographers assistant before he found happiness in his current vocation. He especially likes to do his job in Mauritius – nowhere else does he find so many motifs as on the "sweetest pearl in the Indian Ocean". This time hes working on a photo book about Mauritius – by land, by water and in the air.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Over the Islands of Africa, Madagascar
programme.desc: Spirits, Kings, Lemurs – Madagascar treats Ami to a multitude of new impressions and spectacular pictures. Director Christian Schidlowski and his team accompanied her on her trip.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Over the Islands of Africa, Sao Tome and Principe
programme.desc: Along with photographer Rui Camilo, we travel to the West African island nation of Sao Tome and Príncipe - in search of images that will capture the soul of this small and beautiful country.

programme.title: Over the Islands of Africa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Over the Islands of Africa, Cape Verde
programme.desc: Cape Verde – the islands of Saudade, of longing. For Stephane and Richard it was a journey full of adventure, unforgettable encounters and magnificent photographs. Director Christian Schidlowski and his team accompanied them on their trip.

programme.title: Myths of the Congo - Apes and Aliens
programme.desc: The Congo, mighty and deep like no other river - yet still a retreat and a habitat for several of our worlds strangest animals. Our closest relatives live deep inside the dense jungles: three of the four giant ape species have made the Congo basin their home. Rich in extraordinary footage, the second episode of "Myths of the Congo" also presents exciting insights into one of the most mysterious and dangerous regions on earth.

programme.title: Myths of the Congo - Deep and Dangerous
programme.desc: The river that swallows all rivers - this is what the natives call it. In reality, the Congo, when considering its water masses, is the second largest and the deepest river in the world. At its source in the north of Zambia, it starts out as a mere trickle, but on its journey westwards it grows and grows, becoming ever mightier and with it, the animals, too: the shoebill stork hides in the dense papyrus. Metre-long pythons hunt for their prey in trees and huge hippos fight for power and respect in the water. To survive in the Congo, animals have to adapt to extreme conditions. Here, evolution has spawned unique creatures: fish with lungs, wings and those that go hunting on land. The Congo...

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The Parque Nacional Peneda-Geres is the only national park in Portugal. An area of almost 700 square kilometers, located in the extreme north of Portugal. Barren and rocky ridges in the plateaus, contrast with large forests and lush ground vegetation in deep valleys, crossed by lakes and rivers. The park is known for its oak forests, which are predominantly pedunculate and Pyrenean oaks. Among the typical animals of the park are the small Garrano ponies, a very old breed of horse and the only one in Europe that still lives in the wild.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The highest mountain range in Portugal is the Serra da Estrela. The episode embarks on a voyage of discovery to adventurous rock formations and villages steeped in tradition. The nature park is the largest protected area on the Iberian peninsula. In the mountain range we accompany the young scientist Ana Matos, who wants to breathe new life into old traditions, and cheese maker Maria Natália Lopes. She watches over more than 350 sheeps.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 South West Portugal: Alentejano and Costa Vicentina
programme.desc: In the southwest of Portugal lies the little known Parque Natural do Sudoeste Alentejano e Costa Vicentina. It encompasses a narrow coastal strip that runs along the coast to the south of Portugal. Sparsely populated, this coastal region, which was placed under protection in 1988, is considered one of the last intact ecosystems in Europe. The steep cliffs, the almost constant wind and high waves have ensured that mass tourism has not gained a foothold here. There are still near-natural forests and a diverse bird life.

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: Survival of the Fittest in the Alps
programme.desc: The documentary shows the survival strategies of various animal species in the high mountains of the Alps in winter. Despite freezing temperatures and limited food supply, chamois, red deer and snow hares manage to survive the cold months. Latest research reveals the amazing abilities the animals have developed to adapt to the extreme conditions and also how climate change is altering the behaviour of the alpine inhabitants.

programme.title: Alpine Whistleblowers - On the Playground of the Marmots
programme.desc: These peculiar and roughly rabbit-sized rodents enjoy great popularity at the GroSSglockner in the Austrian Alps. Before the last ice age, marmots used to live in the lowland of Tirol, but with the melting of the glaciers they were driven higher up into the mountains – a trend that will continue given the current climate change. Today, they simply feel too warm below 800 meters. In spring, as soon as the temperatures begin to rise, marmots leave their dens after a nearly six-month long hibernation. After eating their share and recovering from the long fast, losing up to a third of their body weight, the most important thing is founding a family. And that sometimes involves rather fierce...

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Bavaria - In The Shadow of the Watzmann.
programme.desc: Mighty and mysterious, King Watzmann sits above Germanys only alpine national park.

programme.title: Winter Journey to the Polar Circle (Exploring Norway on the Nordlandsbanen)
programme.desc: The Nordland Railway in Norway, travels from Trondheim through the isolated regions of Trendelag and Nordland. After Mo I Rana, it traverses the Arctic Circle and ends in the northern Norwegian town of Bodø. The railway covers a distance of some 729 kilometres, passing by dense, snow-covered forests, frozen fjords and snow-capped mountains. Temperatures of sometimes minus 30 degrees are quite normal here for months, on many days there is no more than five hours of daylight. Kindergarten teacher Kaia Aarstrand und her husband, Bjørnar, a technician for the municipality, live with their four boys in Aursletta, deep within the Vistenfjord, far away from civilization. programme.title: mareTV: Corsica - Fascinating Mountain World in the Mediterranean
programme.desc: Corsica looks like an alpine landscape in the Mediterranean, an island with dramatic rock formations, romantic bays and proud inhabitants who see themselves first and foremost as Corsicans and only then as French. The Greeks in ancient times called the island Kalliste: the beautiful. We explore this fascinating mountain world in the Mediterranean.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Americas National Parks - Grand Canyon
programme.desc: The Grand Canyon is a steep-sided canyon carved by the Colorado River in Arizona, United States. The Grand Canyon is 277 miles (446 km) long, up to 18 miles (29 km) wide and attains a depth of over a mile (6,093 feet or 1,857 meters). The canyon and adjacent rim are contained within Grand Canyon National Park, the Kaibab National Forest, Grand Canyon–Parashant National Monument, the Hualapai Indian Reservation, the Havasupai Indian Reservation and the Navajo Nation. President Theodore Roosevelt was a major proponent of preservation of the Grand Canyon area and visited it on numerous occasions to hunt and enjoy the scenery.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Americas National Parks - Gates of the Arctic
programme.desc: Gates of the Arctic National Park and Preserve is an American national park that protects portions of the Brooks Range in northern Alaska. The park is the northernmost national park in the United States, situated entirely north of the Arctic Circle. The park is the second largest in the US, slightly larger in area than Belgium. Gates of the Arctic was initially designated as a national monument on December 1, 1978, before being redesignated as a national park and preserve upon passage of the Alaska National Interest Lands Conservation Act in 1980. A large part of the park has additional protection as the Gates of the Arctic Wilderness that adjoins the Noatak Wilderness. They form the...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Americas National Parks - Great Smoky Mountains
programme.desc: Great Smoky Mountains National Park is an American national park in the southeastern United States, with parts in Tennessee and North Carolina. The park straddles the ridgeline of the Great Smoky Mountains, part of the Blue Ridge Mountains, which are a division of the larger Appalachian Mountain chain. The park contains some of the highest mountains in eastern North America, including Clingmans Dome, Mount Guyot, and Mount Le Conte. The border between the two states runs northeast to southwest through the center of the park. The Appalachian Trail passes through the center of the park on its route from Georgia to Maine. With 12.5 million visitors in 2019, the Great Smoky Mountains National...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Americas National Parks - Yellowstone
programme.desc: Yellowstone National Park is an American national park located in the western United States, largely in the northwest corner of Wyoming and extending into Montana, and Idaho. It was established by the U.S. Congress and signed into law by President Ulysses S. Grant on March 1, 1872. Yellowstone was the first national park in the U.S. and is also widely held to be the first national park in the world. The park is known for its wildlife and its many geothermal features, especially Old Faithful geyser, one of its most popular. While it represents many types of biomes, the subalpine forest is the most abundant. It is part of the South Central Rockies forests ecoregion.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Americas National Parks - Yosemite
programme.desc: Yosemite National Park is a place of superlatives: with towering cliffs and giant sequoias, home to coyotes, black bears and the most elusive of all: the bobcat. Watch this documentary with ist spectacular shots, aerial views and time-lapse shots and learn some new facts about the biodiversity in one of North Americas most spectacular National Parks.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Americas National Parks - Saguaro
programme.desc: Saguaro National Park is an American national park in Pima County, southeastern Arizona. The 92,000-acre (37,000 ha) park consists of two separate areas—the Tucson Mountain District (TMD) about 10 miles west of the city of Tucson and the Rincon Mountain District (RMD) about 10 miles east of the city—that preserve Sonoran Desert landscapes, fauna, and flora, including the giant saguaro cactus.An inventory of medium and large mammals in the park confirmed the presence of 30 species in Saguaro National Park between 1999 and 2008. Of these, 21 were found in the Tucson Mountain District and 29 in the Rincon Mountain District. A partial list of the parks mammals includes cougars, coyotes,...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Americas National Parks - Olympic
programme.desc: Olympic National Park is an American national park located in the State of Washington, on the Olympic Peninsula. The park has four regions: the Pacific coastline, alpine areas, the west side temperate rainforest and the forests of the drier east side. Within the park there are three distinct ecosystems which are subalpine forest and wildflower meadow, temperate forest, and the rugged Pacific coast. President Theodore Roosevelt originally designated Mount Olympus National Monument on 2 March 1909. The monument was redesignated as a national park by Congress and President Franklin Roosevelt on June 29, 1938. In 1976, Olympic National Park was designated by UNESCO as an International...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Americas National Parks - Everglades
programme.desc: North America’s National Parks are world famous and their breathtaking landscapes fascinate millions of visitors. This spectacular series will show you what happens beyond the lookouts. Everglades National Park is an American national park that protects the southern twenty percent of the original Everglades in Florida. The park is the largest tropical wilderness in the United States, and the largest wilderness of any kind east of the Mississippi River. An average of one million people visit the park each year. Everglades is the third-largest national park in the contiguous United States after Death Valley and Yellowstone. UNESCO declared the Everglades and Dry Tortugas Biosphere Reserve in...

He lives with his family on a remote highland plateau in the Middle Atlas. Lachsen is proud because his 18-year old son Mohammed wants to follow in his father’s footsteps. For that he needs his own horse, so the tradition goes. Lachsen wants to fulfil this dream for his son. programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Under the Spell of the Horses - Iceland
programme.desc: Iceland, the island of longing in the North. The biggest volcanic island in the world is known for its grandiose landscape, for its geysers and glaciers. But it is even more famous for its horses. Icelandic horses are considered the liveliest horses in the whole of Europe with the greatest stamina. They tolt over mossy banks and lava rock unfazed by rivers, glaciers and scree slopes. In Nordic mythology the steed are never far behind the warriors. Where would Siefgried be without his horse Grani, or Odin without Sleipnir. Even the sun wouldn’t rise or set if “awake early” and “very quick” weren’t pulling their chariot. From the beginning of colonisation, the Icelanders had the kind of...

programme.desc: Proud elegance, silky-shiny coats and a graceful, powerful physique – the supreme Marwari horses have been worshipped in India as magical creatures for thousands of years. People say they descended directly from the Gods, that once when the Gods were sitting round the fire, there was so much soot that one of the Gods had to cry. One of the tears from his right eye changed into a stallion, and one of his tears from the left eye produced a mare. Ever since, the people in Rajasthan have believed that horses are Gods. programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. The teenager has been stabbed sixty times with a knife and -an extra sordid detail - a devil mask is found next to her body. Was Priscillia the victim of a prowler? A serial killer? A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. The man is lying in a pool of blood and, on his belly, the murderer has written "DIRTY RAPIST". Yet Jean-Raymond Blatti was never charged with sexual assault. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. The teenager has been stabbed sixty times with a knife and -an extra sordid detail - a devil mask is found next to her body. Was Priscillia the victim of a prowler? A serial killer? A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. The man is lying in a pool of blood and, on his belly, the murderer has written "DIRTY RAPIST". Yet Jean-Raymond Blatti was never charged with sexual assault. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 19th 2004, the naked and tied up body of a woman is recovered in the Ourcq canal in Fresnes-sur-Marne. The victim is impossible to identify.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On April 3th 2003, Chantal Ternik, a 48 year old housewife, is discovered hanged in her house of Sanary-sur-Mer, in Var.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On March 28th 2013, the burnt body of Anne Barbot, 38 years old, is discovered in a forest of Maine-et-Loire.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On May 17th 2005, a body is discovered in a forest of Sucy-en-Brie; Christophe Belle, 40 years old, a renowned pastry cook.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On October 13th 1996, the body of young Angelique Dumetz, 18 years old, is recovered down a ditch in Oise forest. An important clue is found on the crime scene.

programme.title: Camp X-Ray
programme.desc: Kristen Stewart spelar huvudrollen i Peter Sattlers hyllade debutfilm Camp X-Ray. Hon spelar Amy Cole, en ung kvinna som tar varvning i amerikanska militaren i tron att hon kommer att skickas till Irak eller Afghanistan. Istallet blir hon stationerad som vakt på ett okant militarfangelse, med tuffa villkor for såval basens fångar som de få kvinnliga militarer som arbetar dar.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Zalava
programme.desc: 1978, i den avlagsna bergsbyn Zalava ar byborna skrackslagna infor en osynlig fara. De havdar att en demon hemsoker deras by och har anlitat en exorcist for att driva bort anden. Nar den unge sergeanten Massoud griper exorcisten for bedrageri urartar situationen av bybornas skrack och ilska.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Auggie
programme.desc: Felix Greystone har en bit kvar till pensionsåldern, men foretaget pressar honom att gå i fortidspension. I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: The Rum Diary
programme.desc: Den rastlose New York-journalisten Paul trottnar på storstaden och soker sig till Karibien dar han får arbete på en tidningsredaktion som kampar for sin overlevnad i Puerto Rico. Oberakneliga kolleger och en fientligt installd lokalbefolkning blir snart hans vardag, liksom långa blota natter på de otaliga barerna. En natt moter Paul Chenault och blir besatt av den vackra kvinnan, som visar sig vara forlovad med den korrumperade affarsmannen Sanderson. Sanderson inser att han kan ha anvandning av Paul genom att betala honom att skriva fordelaktigt om ett av hans obskyra projekt – att bygga lyxhotell på en orord o vid kusten.

programme.title: Klanen - berattelsen om Grudornas slakt
programme.desc: "Klanen" ar historien om en brottslig slakt dar Mika Kaurismaki behandlar existensens villkor genom den traditionella episka formen, på gransen mellan ratt och fel i lagen. Alexander, den yngsta sonen, ar slaktens vita får. Han forvantas hålla sig på den raka vagen, till skillnad från sin far och andra man i slakten. Men familjen ar varst, och blod ar tjockare an vatten... Familjedramat "Klanen" ar en storslagen hyllning till den gamla finska filmen.

programme.title: The Honor List
programme.desc: Tre fore detta basta vanner återforenas nar den fjarde medlemmen av gruppen plotsligt går bort under sista året i high school. De bestammer sig for att fullfolja den bucket list de gjorde forsta året i high school, nar de fyra annu stod varandra nara.

programme.title: The Truth Commissioner
programme.desc: En sanningskommissionar avslojar morka hemligheter i Nordirland, dar makt och forflutet kolliderar i kampen for rattvisa och forsoning.

programme.title: The Good Heart
programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: Promised Land
programme.desc: Det har dramat foljer två skolkamrater, Hancock och Danny, efter examen. Hancock och hans flickvan som ar en cheerleader ger sig ivag till medelklassens tillhåll utom rackhåll for Danny och hans psykotiska fru Bev.

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Chosen
programme.desc: Året ar 1944 och tusentals judar i Östeuropa dodas. Efter sin frus bortgång startar den ungerske advokaten Sonson en inspirerande kamp mot de alltmer desperata och farliga nazisterna. Med både frackhet och stort mod vander han kampen att overleva till någonting betydligt storre – ett satt att hamnas sitt folks dod genom att radda tusentals andra.

programme.title: Synchronicity
programme.desc: "Fysikern Jim Beale har uppfunnit en maskin som kommer att revolutionera varlden som vi kanner den: en tidsresemaskin som kroker rumtid. Nar Klaus Meisner, en av varldens maktigaste foretagare, får veta det så beslutar han att han till varje pris måste ha maskinen. Nar Jim med maskinen oppnar ett maskhål så dyker det upp en dahlia från framtiden. For att behålla ratten till sin uppfinning måste Jim bevisa att maskinen fungerar genom att hitta blommans identiska motsvarighet i nuet. Jim upptacker snart att dahlian ags av Abby, en mystisk kvinna som forfor honom for att han ska avsloja sina hemligheter.

programme.title: Mazes and Monsters
programme.desc: Robbie och hans collegekompisar ar alla besatta av rollspelet "Mazes and Monsters". Men spelen tar en marklig vandning nar Robbie borjar få visioner efter att de spelat en session på ett mystiskt, lokalt landmarke.

programme.title: The Good Heart
programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: Shattered Glass
programme.desc: Hayden Christensen spelar huvudrollen i denna kritikerrosade berattelse om en utskamd journalist, regisserad och samskriven av Billy Ray, Oscar®-nominerad forfattare av KAPTEN PHILLIPS. Nar den beromda journalisten Stephen Glass (Christensen) plotsligt utredas av en Forbes.com-reporter (Steve Zahn) avslojar sokandet att Glass har diktat ihop många av sina sensationella berattelser, vilket leder till hans ultimata fall i detta gripande, faktabaserade drama.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: Brain On Fire
programme.desc: Susannah Cahalan har nyligen avslutat sina universitetsstudier och lever dromlivet i New York. Hon ar en lovande journalist på New York Post och foralskad i musikern Stephen. Hennes chef ger henne det stora uppdraget som ska rivstarta hennes karriar och livet kan inte bli battre. Snart borjar saker och ting gå fel. Susannah drabbas av en influensa som inte vill ge sig, hon glommer saker och missar deadlines på jobbet. Hon hor att folk pratar om henne, ar overtygad om att Stephen har en annan flickvan och hon kan inte kontrollera sin kropp. Det blir snart varre; Susannah borjar få våldsamma anfall och hennes alltmer psykotiska upptradande innebar att hon standigt måste overvakas.

programme.title: A Woman In Berlin
programme.desc: Våren 1945. Andra varldskriget narmar sig slutet då den roda armen marscherar in i Berlin. En kvinnlig journalist och fotograf som går under namnet Anonyma har tillbringat krigets sista månader i en kallare tillsammans med andra kvinnor som gommer sig i den sonderbombade staden. Efter att ha klarat sig undan krigetsharjningar står de ångestfyllda kvinnorna framfor ryska soldater som betraktar dem som krigsbyten. Desperat efter att finna någon som kan beskydda henne mot befrielsestyrkans systematiska misshandel och våldtakter narmar sig Anonyma en rysk officer och inleder ett forbjudet forhållande…

programme.title: Ingen nåd sa Moses (The Troublemakers)
programme.desc: Travis (Terence Hills) ar vastens snabbaste revolverskytt. Hans bror Moses (Bud Spencer) ar stor som en bjorn och dubbelt så argsint og nybyggartrakternas mest hårdfora prisjagare. Når deras kara gamla mamma beslutar att återforena sina soner till jul blir det Travis uppgift att forsoka locka med sig Moses hem…

programme.title: A Christmas Horror Story
programme.desc: Vaver samman fem komiska berattelser om skrack och ondskefulla julandar.

programme.title: P2
programme.desc: En kvinna som jobbar sent på julafton blir tillfångatagen av en psykotisk sakerhetsvakt som ar besatt av henne. Med inga andra manniskor i parkeringshuset måste hon anvanda all sin list och styrka for att overleva och ta sig darifrån.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Another Christmas Coincedence
programme.desc: Alice och Jack, två framlingar med totalt olika bakgrunder hamnar av en slump en helg på samma brollop. Det klickar direkt mellan dem men Alice ar tveksam till en ny relation efter ett havererat långdistansforhållande. Uppmuntrad av mamma Olga borjar Alice sakta vanja sig med tanken och borja dejta igen. Mer tillfalligheterna for dem narmare samtidigt som nya hinder avloser varann och utmanar den nyfunna romansen.

programme.title: My Christmas Inn
programme.desc: Nar affarskvinnan Jennifer får reda på att hennes foraldrar tanker resa bort over julen utan henne, bestammer hon sig for att lamna sitt hektiska storstadsliv i San Francisco for att besoka Grandmas Inn i Alaska, ett vardshus som hon har arvt for att renovera och sedan salja.

programme.title: 12 Pups of Christmas
programme.desc: Erin har precis avslutat ett forhållande och laddar for omstart med nytt jobb i en ny stad. Men just nar hon trodde att hon landat springer hon på den sjalvcentriske bossen Martin. Han kampar med att hålla sitt foretag vid liv och ber Erin om hjalp att ta hand om 12st valpar som lamnats kvar efter ett jobb precis lagom innan jul. Ju mer de jobbar med varann strommar kanslorna fram och karlek uppstår just lagom till den stundande hogtiden.

programme.title: Guess Whos Coming To Christmas Dinner?
programme.desc: Den aktivistiska, liberala och progressiva juridikstudenten Maya tar med sin nya pojkvan hem for julen utan att beratta for familjen att han ar vit. Gissa vem som kommer till julmiddag?

programme.title: En Jadrans Jul
programme.desc: En hund med telepatiska formågor undkommer en regeringskontroll- och springer rakt i armarna på två unga broder. Men Washington-hojdarna ger inte upp sitt hemliga vapen så latt.

programme.title: Deck the Halls
programme.desc: Den har deckaren baseras på boken av den bastsaljande mysterieforfattaren Mary Higgins Clark. En kvinnlig detektiv slår sig samman med en amatordetektiv for att hitta sin forsvunna pappa.

programme.title: So This Is Christmas
programme.desc: Unga Ashley håller på att kora i diket med sitt liv och hanger ute med helt fel personer i forsok att fly undan allt familjedrama. Plotsligt verkar allt byta riktning då hantverkaren de anlitat uppmuntrar henne att satta upp en jul pjas for opriviligerade ungdomar. Ashley ser sin chans att heala sin egen problemfyllda familj genom att uppmuntra andra i battre behov av hjalp. Tillsammans upptacker de fantastiska av vad man enkelt kan åstakomma genom den underbara gåvan att bara kunna ge till andra.

programme.title: Sander jul
programme.desc: Nar hennes on-air-partner bestammer sig for att lamna Amerikas favoritmorgonprogram, meddelar Veronika Daniels att hon kommer att valja sin nya medvard bland en handfull kandidater som inkluderar Charlie Fisher, en lokal nyhetsupplasare i NY.

programme.title: En Bennett-sång Holiday
programme.desc: Familjen Bennett-Song återvander till jul med stora nyheter. Mrs Song vantar ett barn som ska utoka listan på 14 adopterade barn! Familjen måste samarbeta for att ta sig an en maktig byggherre- som vill stanga farbrors kulturhus for handikappade och utsatta barn. Lite karlek, lagarbete och julmagi kommer att radda dagen.

programme.title: P2
programme.desc: En kvinna som jobbar sent på julafton blir tillfångatagen av en psykotisk sakerhetsvakt som ar besatt av henne. Med inga andra manniskor i parkeringshuset måste hon anvanda all sin list och styrka for att overleva och ta sig darifrån.

programme.title: A Christmas Horror Story
programme.desc: Vaver samman fem komiska berattelser om skrack och ondskefulla julandar.

programme.title: High Holiday
programme.desc: Den frisinnade Liz ar inte så sugen på att ta med sin pojkvan hem till sin konservativa familj på julmiddag. Liz pojkvan foreslår att hon ska krydda salladsdressingen med marijuana for att latta upp stamningen. Kaos uppstår nar alla blir omedvetet hoga och avslojar familjens innersta hemligheter.

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsakringsman som kampar med forlust och karlek upptacker nya mojligheter under en vecka full av ovantade handelser och komiska vandpunkter.

programme.title: Tyler Perrys a Madea Christmas
programme.desc: Madea sprider sin alldeles egen unika julstamning nar hon blir overtalad att spendera julen ute på landet med en van och hennes familj.

programme.title: En Jadrans Jul
programme.desc: En hund med telepatiska formågor undkommer en regeringskontroll- och springer rakt i armarna på två unga broder. Men Washington-hojdarna ger inte upp sitt hemliga vapen så latt.

programme.title: 12 Gifts of Christmas
programme.desc: Nar Anna, en arbetslos konstnar, inte får ihop ekonomin, anlitas hon som personal jul-shopper åt Marc, en spand bolagschef.

programme.title: My Christmas Inn
programme.desc: Nar affarskvinnan Jennifer får reda på att hennes foraldrar tanker resa bort over julen utan henne, bestammer hon sig for att lamna sitt hektiska storstadsliv i San Francisco for att besoka Grandmas Inn i Alaska, ett vardshus som hon har arvt for att renovera och sedan salja.

programme.title: A Christmas in Royal Fashion
programme.desc: Kristin Cooper, den sota och talangfulla assistenten på en global PR-firma, får ansvar for den årliga julmodeshowen och auktionen for en kladentreprenor, mr Carson.

programme.title: Julkupong
programme.desc: En fore detta skridskomastare borjar undervisa vid sin vans damm- och delar ut "kuponger" for att locka nya elever. Nar hennes fore detta ungdomskarlek (och nu kand hockeyspelare) tar med sin brorsdotter på lektioner, tands gamla flammor på nytt, och julen fylls med en andra chans for karlek.

programme.title: Julmuffins
programme.desc: Nar familjebageriet kanske måste stanga strax fore jul- måste systrarna Kim och Gina tavla om att vinna det stora priset. I en varld av hårda konkurrenter och en tickande klocka- kravs det ett julmirakel for att radda bageriet. Men de kan upptacka ett pris som ar storre an de hoppats på.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Stilla natt, heliga natt - Joseph Mohrs heroiska resa 1818, nar han skapade varldens mest kanda julsång. Den sanna historien om låten berattas som en fiktiv historia.

programme.title: Bonden och Belle: Radda Santaland
programme.desc: Nar en kand modell återvander till sin småstad fore jul- traffar hon sin barndomsvan som nu har en dotter och en gård. Det slår snart gnistor mellan dem- och hon borjar lara sig att akta karlek och skonhet kommer inifrån. Men staden riskerar att forlora sin alskade Santaland-festival- men de upptacker att mirakel kan ske med beslutsamhet och tro.

programme.title: Jul under Wraps
programme.desc: CHRISTMAS UNDER WRAPS, med Candace Cameron Bure som Dr Lauren Brunell som accepterar en position i Alaska efter att ha forlorat både sin pojkvan och prestigefyllda operationsstipendium, bara for att få veta att det ar ett litet sjukhus i en liten stad.

programme.title: Philippines
programme.desc: The nation of 7,000 islands has no problems with beach, sun, or sea; but they suffer tremendously with cuisine image. Jonathan lands in Manila to discover the top chefs are well aware of the issue and, following their advice, he launches off on an expedition to find part of the solution. Driving from headhunting tribal villages, to step-back-in-time colonial towns, to restaurants in the shadow of the American military behemoth an intriguing story slowly pieces together. In the dense jungle one treasure stays buried while another comes literally out of the woodwork. But danger always lurks.. zombie moray eels, landslide prone passes, and forbidden fields behind the rice paddies.

However, the reserved Finns have been quietly perfecting their craft of foraging culture and incorporating it into their unique cuisine. Jonathan Legg explores the entire expanse of the country to understand it’s cuisine, and the ethos of the country’s top chefs; from amazing locally sourced cuisine in Helsinki, to an expedition in Lapland to learn about foraging and the Finnish delicacy, reindeer!

Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

Fraser (The Last of the Clintons, Rustlers Paradise) directs a strong cast of familiar faces, including legendary sidekick George Gabby Hayes, Earl Dwyer, and one of the hardest ridin stuntmen turned actors, Yakima Canutt.

Also, be on the lookout for the beautiful Christine McIntyre, who would go on to appear in several of the Three Stooges shorts for Colombia Pictures.

Directed by B-movie legend Sam Newfield for Excelsior Pictures, this film is a showcase for McCoy, who appeared in more than 90 movies and in 1960 earned a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame!

Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West.
